00:00:56.956 --> 00:00:59.091
<i> Of course, reality is
 these are bears at</i>

00:00:59.091 --> 00:01:00.627
<i>basically a Hollywood facility.</i>

00:01:00.627 --> 00:01:04.030
<i>They train bears to fake roar
and fake maul for the movies.</i>

00:01:04.030 --> 00:01:06.399
