so that's all there is to it.

00:01:12.939 --> 00:01:14.507
<i> So, I loaded up as
 much as I could</i>

00:01:14.507 --> 00:01:16.409
<i> for that week,
anything I could think up.</i>

00:01:16.409 --> 00:01:18.544
<i> And when I did go
 to Alaska finally.</i>

00:01:18.544 --> 00:01:20.913
<i>I went to the most visually
loaded place that I could find</i>

00:01:20.913 --> 00:01:22.482
<i>where I knew the bears were.</i>

00:01:22.482 --> 00:01:23.716
<i>So, what's the story here?</i>

00:01:23.716 --> 00:01:26.452
<i> Well, bears actually
 tolerate us just fine.</i>

00:01:26.452 --> 00:01:27.787
<i> We can't stand bears.</i>

00:01:27.787 --> 00:01:30.089
<i> Bears love our garbage,
full of food and good smells,</i>

00:01:30.089 --> 00:01:31.023
<i> but...</i>

00:01:31.224 --> 00:01:34.260
they get a little aggressive,
get into our dumpsters

00:01:34.260 --> 00:01:37.162
they get into our bird-feeders
next and our dog food.

00:01:37.162 --> 00:01:38.631
They break into our cabins and--

00:01:38.631 --> 00:01:40.032
<i>A fed bear is a dead bear.</i>

00:01:40.032 --> 00:01:41.701
<i> They end up getting
 shot and sold</i>

00:01:41.701 --> 00:01:44.603
<i>at the state of Alaska surplus
sale, twice a year in Alaska.</i>

00:01:44.603 --> 00:01:47.506
So, with bears it's fairly
straight forward, you know

00:01:47.506 --> 00:01:49.942
keep them out of the garbage,
everything is gonna be okay.

00:01:49.942 --> 00:01:51.010
They're, you know,
they don't--

00:01:51.177 --> 00:01:53.312
they kill one person a year on
the North American continent

00:01:53.312 --> 00:01:54.981
so they tend to get
a very bad rap

00:01:54.981 --> 00:01:58.718
even though we lose many times
that to domestic dog fatalities

00:01:58.718 --> 00:01:59.985
every year in this country.

00:01:59.985 --> 00:02:01.854
<i> What about the more
 quiet species?</i>

00:02:01.854 --> 00:02:03.022
<i> What about wolves?</i>

00:02:03.122 --> 00:02:05.858
<i>They're more of an enigma and
this is the problem with wolves</i>

00:02:05.858 --> 00:02:07.660
<i> because people want to
 view them either as</i>

00:02:07.660 --> 00:02:11.330
