We're cued every
minute of every day

00:02:16.235 --> 00:02:18.904
how to think about everything,
from our news to

00:02:18.904 --> 00:02:21.274
who's good and who's bad
in any reality show.

00:02:21.274 --> 00:02:23.276
<i> But with most wildlife,
 including predators</i>

